        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: GRB2 was detected in crude synaptic vesicle fractions prepared from Rat brain (Figure 1). Various synaptic GRB2 interactors are indentified; Sos1, Dynamin, Synapsin1 and p145/Synaptojanin1 (PMID:7982917).. Experimental description: M&M: \"Synaptic fractions were prepared from rat brain as described\"" ;
